## Summary of Changes Made:

### 1. Algorithms.tsx - Major Enhancement
- Added 7 new sorting/searching algorithms: Heap Sort, Radix Sort, Dijkstra's, A* Search, Binary Search variants
- Added code implementation tab with JavaScript and Python code
- Added complexity comparison charts using Recharts
- Added interactive coding playground
- Added algorithm selection guide with complexity table
- Added use cases and interview tips for each algorithm

### 2. MockInterview.tsx - New Page
- AI-powered mock interview system
- Technical, Behavioral, and System Design questions
- Difficulty levels (Easy, Medium, Hard)
- Timer for each question
- AI-generated feedback with ratings
- Session history tracking
- Progress visualization

### 3. ResumeAnalyzer.tsx - New Page
- AI-powered resume analysis
- Overall score and ATS compatibility scoring
- Section-by-section analysis
- Keyword analysis (found/missing)
- Job match percentage
- Improvement suggestions with priority
- Export report functionality

### 4. App.tsx - Updated
- Added imports for MockInterview and ResumeAnalyzer
- Added routes for /mock-interview and /resume-analyzer

### 5. Sidebar.tsx - Updated
- Added Mock Interview navigation item
- Added Resume Analyzer navigation item
- Added Brain and FileText icons
